# Runtime-local directories can contain generated install output, caches,
# installed packages, logs, and user-specific state. Keep them ignored by
# default.
#
# The Codex marketplace catalog is the exception: it is a repo-scoped source
# entry, not user-local install state.
.agents/*
!.agents/plugins/
!.agents/plugins/marketplace.json

.codex/
.opencode/

__pycache__/
*.pyc
